2:T6d0,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Crisp better than Help Scout?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Crisp scores 7.0 overall while Help Scout scores 8.0. Crisp is best for startups and small teams, while Help Scout excels for small businesses and SaaS startups."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Crisp or Help Scout?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Crisp starts at Free and Help Scout starts at $50/mo. Crisp offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Crisp to Help Scout?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Crisp and Help Scout support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Crisp vs Help Scout?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Crisp holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Help Scout has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Crisp for generous free plan and Help Scout for clean and simple shared inbox."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Crisp or Help Scout?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Help Scout for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Crisp remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize generous free plan. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className"